These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, trike, car, subway
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
2. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | subway | snowmobile | trike | car |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, dancing, fishing, gardening
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is baking##5
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | baking | gardening | dancing | fishing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman, paramedic, manager
1. the fisherman is on the right of the paramedic##1
2. the fisherman is on the far left or far right##3
3. the project-manager is the project-manager##1
4. the project-manager is somewhere to the right of the manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | manager | project-manager | paramedic | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, singing, board-games, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | singing | board-games | hiking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, martial-arts, superhero
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | mystery | superhero | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
