3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | photography | dancing | filmmaking | drawing |

