2. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
3. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
