.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, hedgehog, mouse
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | mouse | bird | ferret | hedgehog |

